<p class="ayah 34-22" id="22" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">قُلِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Say,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱدْعُواْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">`Call upon</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلَّذِينَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">those whom</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">زَعَمْتُم</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">you claim</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مِّن دُونِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">besides</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱللَّهِۖ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Allah.`</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Not</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يَمْلِكُونَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">they possess</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مِثْقَالَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(the) weight</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ذَرَّةٍ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(of) an atom</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فِى</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">in</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلسَّمَـٰوَٲتِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the heavens</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl"