<p class="ayah 34-24" id="24" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">۞ قُلْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Say,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مَن</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">`Who</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يَرْزُقُكُم</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">provides (for) you</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مِّنَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">from</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلسَّمَـٰوَٲتِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the heavens</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَٱلْأَرْضِۖ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and the earth?`</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">قُلِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Say,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱللَّهُۖ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">`Allah.</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَإِنَّآ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">And indeed, we</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَوْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">or</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِيَّاكُمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">you</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لَعَلَىٰ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(are) surely upon</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="r